DESCRIPTION:

  Fasten your seatbelts for the ride of your life.  JAZZ JACKRABBIT is
  coming towards you at light speed, and this little bunny carries a
  big gun! The evil turtle emperor Devan Shell has rabbitnapped the
  bunny-babe princess Eva Earlong.  Now he's swiping all the goodies in the
  galaxy to support his plot of Galactic Rabbit Destruction!  Lead the
  speedy Jazz on a wild treasure hunt spanning enormous areas with perilous
  dangers. 

  ULTRA-SMOOTH scrolling 256 color graphics, ROCKING Digital Audio with
  Surround Sound, and WHITE-HOT action from Epic MegaGames!

REQUIRES:

  * 33-Mhz or faster 80386 processor
  * 4 Megabytes of memory

ALSO SUPPORTS:

  * Joystick, Gravis Gamepad
  * Sound Blaster, SB Pro, SB-16, PAS-16, Gravis Ultrasound sound cards

